programme.title: Joel Osteen S3
programme.desc: Hear the messages of hope that best-selling author, evangelist and the senior pastor of Lakewood Church in Houston, Joel Osteen is delivering in each episode. Joel's positive and encouraging speeches will allow viewers to hear God's message of hope, love and victory and be inspired to do great things in life. Joel tries to teach Biblical principles in a simple way, always highlighting the power and importance of love and positive thinking.

programme.title: Secret Lives of the Super Rich (Record-shattering Mansion & Private Jet Makeover) S1 (n°611)
programme.desc: «Record-shattering Mansion & Private Jet Makeover»Get an exclusive sneak peek at the $500 million mega-mansion that's about to become the biggest and most expensive home to ever hit the market in the U.S. Meet the super-rich couple transforming their private jet into a flying haven for their dogs. Check out Miami's hottest new building where a special elevator delivers your supercar to the middle of your living room. Behold the world's largest uncut diamond, a rare rock that glows in the dark. Step inside a tech titan's magnificent California mansion. See why watch collectors are spending seven figures on quirky timepieces with an "out-of-this-world" twist. Live like pop royalty inside Taylor Swift's historic Manhattan manor. See why the ultra-wealthy swear by the world's most expensive skin cream, an elixir that goes for $1,800 per ounce.

programme.title: La fièvre du dollar (The insider: Raj Rajaratnam) S1 (n°56)
programme.desc: «The insider: Raj Rajaratnam»It's one of the biggest cases of insider trading in history. Raj Rajaratnam had it all...a wildly successful hedge fund, billions in the bank, and the respect of Wall Street. But behind closed doors, Rajaratnam was gaming the system to the tune of $75 million-dollars!
